name: Trellis
description: Trellis is an open-source multi-chain automated market maker (AMM) protocol for token swaps on Aptos and Sui networks. Trade anonymously. No registration. No signup. No login. No KYC needed. With Trellis you can trade, stake, farm tokens and participate in IDOs of your favorite on Aptos and Sui networks without having to create account or go through any cumbersome KYC procedures.
